data.description: Don't let this one get away!!!!! Just renovated in 2020, this house offers breathtaking mountain views. Its spacious floor plan, flooded with natural light, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Located near central lakeside, this property is sure to capture the hearts of all. Leased Sun Run solar at approximately $145.00 for 14 panels as well as Tesla powerwall. Photos taken prior to current tenant occupying the property.
